author: crogers
msg: Modified the grammar for the declarative validation of a custom rule. The ValidateCustomGrammar no longer requires either "message" or "messageKey" attributes in the @ValidateCustomRule annotation. The msg attribute of the custom rule <validator> element (in validation-rules.xml) is the default message key to use when this validator fails. The "message" and "messageKey" attributes can be used to override the msg.
Also, some minor cleanup - fixed a few typos, etc.
Tests: bvt in netui (WinXP), build.dist and build/test the custom rule validation in netui-samples
